
### `.gitignore`

Create a `.gitignore` file to specify which files and directories Git should ignore. Here's a basic `.gitignore` for an Electron project:

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/

# Logs
*.log

# OS specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Build output
dist/
build/

# Environment files
.env

# npm package lock
package-lock.json

# Electron-specific
*.asar
*.asar.unpacked

# IDE specific files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs_analysis.dat
*.ncb
*.suo
*.sln
*.swp
